programme.desc: Seorang nelayan muda bernama Chin Hu jatuh cinta dengan teman masa kecilnya, Hsiao Yu. Namun, putra satu-satunya preman di sana terpukau pada kecantikan Hsiao Yu dan mencoba segala cara untuk mendekatinya.

programme.title: Disciples Of The 36th Chamber
programme.desc: Legendary martial arts director Lau Kar-leung strikes gold directing half-brother Gordon Liu as golden-robed monk San Te, who reprises his role from The 36th Chamber of Shaolin.

programme.title: Disciples Of The 36th Chamber
programme.desc: Sutradara film bela diri nan legendaris, Lau Kar-leung, menuai pujian saat menyutradarai film yang menampilkan Gordon Liu sebagai San Te si biksu berjubah emas seperti dalam film The 36th Chamber Of Shaolin.

programme.title: Young Vagabond
programme.desc: Beggar Su and his brother train incessantly to defeat the brutally powerful thief called Centipede.

programme.title: Young Vagabond
programme.desc: Pengemis Su dan saudaranya berlatih tanpa henti demi mengalahkan seorang pencuri sadis yang dijuluki Sang Lipan.

programme.title: Torrent Of Desire
programme.desc: David is falling in love with a fashion model Dan Feng and marries her. David's sister Mona is in love with his best friend Han Ming. Out of jealousy, Mona lies to him about a fake affair between Han Ming and Dan Feng.

programme.title: Torrent Of Desire
programme.desc: David jatuh cinta pada Dan Feng dan menikahinya. Saudari David yang bernama Mona jatuh cinta dengan sahabatnya, Han Ming. Karena cemburu, Mona berbohong tentang perselingkuhan antara Han Ming dan Dan Feng.

programme.title: Princess Iron Fan
programme.desc: The Monkey King and his gang are confronted by the evil Princess Iron Fan, Madam White Bone and her two sexy sisters, plus a cast of fanciful characters.

programme.title: Princess Iron Fan
programme.desc: Raja Kera dan gengnya dihadang oleh Putri Kipas Besi yang jahat, Nyonya Tulang Putih dan dua adiknya yang seksi, serta sederet karakter-karakter aneh lainnya.

programme.title: Hong Kong Family
programme.desc: Eight years ago, the family in a Hakka-walled village was torn apart during a combative winter solstice dinner. Eight years later, their cousin returns home from England and seeks to reunite the family for another winter solstice dinner. While things seem to be falling apart, this dinner may well be an opportunity to mend relations.

programme.title: Where The Wind Blows
programme.desc: Detectives Lui Lok and Nam Kong build a corruption system that creates conflicts between the triad and the police. When ICAC hunts down the two, their control finally comes to an end.

programme.title: Where The Wind Blows
programme.desc: Detektif Lui Lok dan Nam Kong membangun sebuah sistem korupsi yang menimbulkan konflik antara anggota geng dan kepolisian. Kekuasaan keduanya pun berakhir saat ICAC melakukan pengejaran terhadap mereka.

programme.title: The Infernal Walker
programme.desc: Ting is an undercover police who infiltrates a triad and Tuen is a triad mole being planted into the police force. While Tang is tired of being an undercover cop, Tuen wishes to quit the triad and become a real police. When the triad boss sets a trap to uncover the moles' identity, the two must fight for themselves.

programme.title: Band Four
programme.desc: An aspiring singer of an indie band called Band Four reunites with her estranged guitarist father following the death of her mother. Together, they support each other through their love and passion for music.

programme.title: Band Four
programme.desc: Seorang vokalis dari band indi bernama Band Four bertemu kembali dengan ayahnya yang seorang gitaris usai sepeninggalan sang ibu. Keduanya pun saling mendukung melalui kecintaan dan kegemaran mereka terhadap musik.

programme.title: My Kung Fu Sweetheart
programme.desc: Phoenixs (Cecilia Cheung) parents are martial arts superheroes, who hide their true identities while ferreting out evil martial artists. Phoenix gets the go-ahead to train in the misty mountains, where she learns of her all-important romantic destiny...

programme.title: The Way We Are
programme.desc: Set in Tin Shui Wai, a marginalised satellite town, Kwai is a middle-aged widow who works hard in a neighbourhood supermarket to support herself and her son. They lead a mundane but fulfilling life. When an elderly woman who lives alone moved in to Tin Shui Wai, Kwai strikes up a friendship with her and helps her ease into a new life.

programme.title: Caught In Time
programme.desc: Based on true events, Detective Zhong Cheng leads a task force in pursuit of Eagle, a criminal gang led by Zhang Sun. Highly methodical and disciplined, the gang manages to avoid capture after each heist. A decade later, the need to stop Eagle is more urgent than ever when Zhong Cheng realizes that his time is almost up to solve the case.

programme.title: A Guilty Conscience
programme.desc: Due to the negligence of sharp-tongued barrister Adrian, his innocent client is convicted of murder and sentenced to 17 years in jail. An opportunity to appeal the case and free his client arises a few years later, but in order to right his wrong, he must fight against one of the most powerful families in Hong Kong for justice to prevail.

programme.title: Chasing The Dragon
programme.desc: Crippled Ho came to Hong Kong as an illegal immigrant in 1963 and ruthlessly carved an empire from the chaotic underworld of drug dealers and corrupt police that ruled the city under notorious detective Lee Rock.

programme.title: Chasing The Dragon
programme.desc: Ho datang ke Hong Kong sebagai imigran gelap pada tahun 1963 dan membangun kerajaan di dunia rahasia para pengedar narkoba dan polisi korup yang memerintah kota di bawah kekuasaan detektif terkenal bernama Lee Rock.

programme.title: Life Must Go On
programme.desc: When the 'midnight gymnasium' programme for wayward teenage girls is at funding risk, social worker Yanki puts together a dodgeball team to compete in a match and save it.

programme.title: Life Must Go On
programme.desc: Saat program 'gimnasium tengah malam' untuk para siswi yang bermasalah menghadapi krisis pendanaan, pekerja sosial Yanki membentuk sebuah tim dodgeball untuk ikut dalam pertandingan guna menyelamatkan program tersebut.

programme.title: Wo Hu
programme.desc: The Hong Kong Police has placed more than a thousand undercover officers in various triad groups to bring down the largest criminal organization in Hong Kong. Betrayal, deceit and murder bring this group of "brothers" into a collision with the law and with each other!

programme.title: Destiny's Champion
programme.desc: Brilliant director Sun Chung and the majestic Ti Lung reunite for a thriller about an aging fighter who relives his violent past mistakes through a streetwise kid.

programme.title: Destiny's Champion
programme.desc: Sun Chung dan Ti Lung bersatu kembali untuk sebuah kisah menegangkan tentang seorang pendekar tua yang berusaha menebus kesalahannya di masa lalu melalui seorang anak jalanan yang bijaksana.

programme.title: The Sparring Partner
programme.desc: A young man partners with his friend to murder and dismember his parents. Pleading not guilty, defense attorneys face each other as nine jurors grapple with the truth.

programme.title: The Sparring Partner
programme.desc: Seorang pemuda bekerja sama dengan temannya untuk membunuh dan memutilasi orang tuanya. Namun, keduanya mengaku tidak bersalah hingga membuat pengacara mereka berselisih saat kesembilan juri berusaha mencerna fakta.

programme.title: Look Out, Officer!
programme.desc: Stephen Chow is a delight in this supernatural action comedy about a murdered cop returning from beyond the grave to persuade a rookie (Chow) into avenging his death.

programme.title: Look Out, Officer!
programme.desc: Stephen Chow is a delight in this supernatural action comedy about a murdered cop returning from beyond the grave to persuade a rookie (Chow) into avenging his death.

programme.title: Detective Dee & Nine-Storey...
programme.desc: A series of strange incidents happen at the Tang's demon building but Detective Dee finds no clue. When the eldest daughter Miss Tang secretly informs Dee about Mr Tang's strange behavior, he vows to unveil the truth.

programme.title: Detective Dee & Nine-Storey...
programme.desc: Detektif Dee kesulitan menangani serangkaian insiden aneh yang terjadi di gedung iblis milik Tang. Ketika putri Tang memberitahunya tentang perilaku aneh sang ayah, ia pun bersumpah akan memecahkan kasus tersebut.

programme.title: Love And Let Love!
programme.desc: Cliff proposes to his girlfriend Terry but is killed in a car accident before she says yes. Terry is devastated and inconsolable. When Cliff's ghost returns, they seem to go back to their good old days. However, Cliff is determined to help Terry get over his death and start anew.

programme.title: From Vegas To Macau
programme.desc: Chow Yun Fat stars as "Magic Hands" Ken, a legendary gambling maestro who is forced out of retirement when his daughter's safety is compromised by an international gambling mafia. In order to save her, Ken and his new protg Cool must work together to expose the evil mastermind by challenging him to a high stakes head-to-head battle of cards.

programme.title: Everything Is Unknown
programme.desc: Pan Yi Ming receives his father's will stating that he must attend his funeral at home to claim the huge inheritance. When he returns home, he encounters his ex-girlfriend, her husband Hua Qi and his daughter whom he has never met.

programme.title: Chasing The Dragon
programme.desc: Crippled Ho came to Hong Kong as an illegal immigrant in 1963 and ruthlessly carved an empire from the chaotic underworld of drug dealers and corrupt police that ruled the city under notorious detective Lee Rock.

programme.title: Chasing The Dragon
programme.desc: Ho datang ke Hong Kong sebagai imigran gelap pada tahun 1963 dan membangun kerajaan di dunia rahasia para pengedar narkoba dan polisi korup yang memerintah kota di bawah kekuasaan detektif terkenal bernama Lee Rock.

programme.title: Men Suddenly In Love
programme.desc: Five high-school alumni - councilor Ng Yuk Yan (Eric Tsang), actor Cheung Chau Wan (Jim Chim), gynecologist Fu Mo Sum (Wong Jing), feng shui master Szeto Kei Fung (Chapman To), and dance coach Charlie Lam (Det Dik) - get together to throw a birthday party for their respected teacher Mr. Chu (Richard Ng), who enlightened them about the birds and the bees. Five delectable young models appear at the party, during which the 80-year-old educator gets too excited and unfortunately kicks the bucket - but not before telling his pupils to fulfill his last wish and get a little naughty! The quintet of married men then takes it upon themselves to conquer the babes, all the while trying to evade the watchful eye of their wives (Maggie Cheung Ho Yee, Yeung Sze Man, Monica Chan, Mak Ling Ling, and Jacqueline Chong).

programme.title: Love Is Blind, Hate Too
programme.desc: Bo lost her eye sight in a serious car accident a year ago. One day, an intruder enters Bo's house and takes her hostage. Then, she discovers her husband's secret which is related to her accident last year.

programme.title: Love Is Blind, Hate Too
programme.desc: Bo menjadi buta karena kecelakaan mobil satu tahun yang lalu. Suatu hari, seorang penyusup masuk ke rumah Bo, menyandera dirinya, dan membuatnya menemukan rahasia sang suami yang terkait dengan kecelakaan tahun lalu.

programme.title: Article 20
programme.desc: A prosecutor on his last case deals with a colleague to exonerate a suspect, making the law just.

programme.title: Article 20
programme.desc: Seorang jaksa penuntut dalam kasus terakhirnya berunding dengan seorang koleganya untuk membebaskan seorang tersangka, membuat hukum menjadi adil.

programme.title: New Kung Fu Cult Master 2
programme.desc: In this sequel, Zhang Wu Ji successfully rescued the Six Major sects at Dadu. Nevertheless, the quest for the Dragon Sabre continues as Wu Ji and his three girlfriends set sail for Ice Fire Island. After a series of vicious fights, they finally unveil the secret behind the Heaven Sword and Dragon Sabre.

programme.title: Shock Wave 2
programme.desc: A series of bomb explosions is causing fear in Hong Kong. Former bomb specialist Feng is found in coma at the crime scene and becomes a suspect. To prove his innocence, he seeks help from his former partner Wen. However, it seems revealing the truth is as risky as disposing a bomb

programme.title: You Are The One
programme.desc: A talented rogue trader experiences a 180-degree change in life when he encounters a girl who does not believe good things will happen to her. Will they fall in love?

programme.title: You Are The One
programme.desc: Seorang pedagang licik namun berbakat mengalami perubahan 180 derajat saat ia bertemu seorang gadis yang tidak percaya bahwa hal-hal baik akan terjadi padanya. Akankah mereka jatuh cinta?

programme.title: Tales From The Occult
programme.desc: An old school anthology consisting of three short films, Tales from the Occult is the first in a new omnibus series about the hidden horrors that lurk behind the urban landscape of Hong Kong.

programme.title: Tales From The Occult
programme.desc: Tales From The Occult merupakan sebuah antologi kuno yang terdiri dari tiga film pendek dan berisi serangkaian kisah baru nan menyeramkan yang tersembunyi di balik suasana perkotaan di Hong Kong.

programme.title: Flirting Scholar 2
programme.desc: The movie tells the story of Tang Bo Hu and his three buddies before they become the four great talents in Jiangnan. Tang Bo Hu encounters a beautiful girl when studying in a monastery and they quickly fall in love, but her hidden identity is accidentally unveiled when Tang and friends uncover a conspiracy at the monastery.

programme.title: The Movie Emperor
programme.desc: Actor Lau Wai-Chi has a huge following of devoted followers and is always keeping an eye on his rivals. After accepting to play the lead in a modest indie drama, Lau begins the laborious process of mastering the acting skills for the role.

programme.title: The Movie Emperor
programme.desc: Actor Lau Wai-Chi has a huge following of devoted followers and is always keeping an eye on his rivals. After accepting to play the lead in a modest indie drama, Lau begins the laborious process of mastering the acting skills for the role.

programme.title: Only Cloud Knows
programme.desc: This romantic drama is based on the story of a real-life couple. It follows a grieving husband as he journeys to places of significance to his beloved dead wife across their New Zealand homeland.

programme.title: Only Cloud Knows
programme.desc: Berdasarkan kisah nyata sepasang suami istri, film ini bercerita tentang perjalanan seorang suami melintasi kampung halaman mereka di Selandia Baru menuju sejumlah tempat yang bermakna bagi mendiang istri tercintanya.

programme.title: Quan Dao: Journey Of A Boxer
programme.desc: When Xing's son attempts drug trafficking to save his father's studio but fails and is brutally beaten up, Ah Niu accepts a death combat challenge so as to help him take revenge.

programme.title: Quan Dao: Journey Of A Boxer
programme.desc: Ketika putra Xing mencoba menjual narkoba untuk menyelamatkan studio ayahnya tapi gagal dan malah dipukuli secara brutal, Ah Niu menerima sebuah tantangan bertarung hingga mati untuk membantunya membalas dendam.

programme.title: Come Back Home
programme.desc: In a chilly winter, De and his family goes on a self-drive tour to Changbai Mountain. The holiday turns tragic when Des eight-year-old son goes missing. He seeks help from the local police but is unable to find his son. Though the golden hour has passed, De and the rescue team insist on continuing the search. Can they finally rescue the boy?

programme.title: Call Me Agent
programme.desc: One day, Miu Ling rescues an injured secret agent who promises to make her his apprentice. From then on, her life is turned upside down and she goes onto a roller-coaster of madcap adventures.

programme.title: Call Me Agent
programme.desc: Suatu hari, Miu Ling menyelamatkan seorang agen rahasia yang terluka dan dijanjikan akan diangkat sebagai muridnya. Sejak saat itu, kehidupannya berubah drastis menjadi sebuah petualangan nan gila.

programme.title: Lan Kwai Fong
programme.desc: Lee is the Production head of an advertising firm who tries to improve her team's performance by competing with Creative head Chan in the day and clubbing at Lan Kwai Fong for ideas at night.

programme.title: Lan Kwai Fong
programme.desc: Menceritakan tentang Lee, Kepala Produksi sebuah agen periklanan yang berusaha meningkatkan kinerja timnya agar dapat mengalahkan Ketua Tim Kreatif Chan dengan dugem di Lan Kwai Fong untuk mendapatkan ide.

programme.title: Europe Raiders
programme.desc: Mr Lin and Miss Wang are the two top bounty hunters in the business, and are searching for the destructive missile Hand of God to prove who is the better bounty hunter. They soon realize they are not the only ones after the missile. Will Lin and Wang put their differences aside and work together in search for the Hand of God?

programme.title: Septet: The Story Of Hong Kong
programme.desc: Seven of Hong Kong's most revered directors, all with distinctly unique styles, come together for the first time to compose a symphony of stories for their city from the 50s to the future.

programme.title: Septet: The Story Of Hong Kong
programme.desc: Untuk pertama kalinya, tujuh sutradara dengan gaya nan unik dan paling dihormati di Hong Kong berkumpul guna menciptakan serangkaian kisah tentang kota Hong Kong dari tahun 50-an hingga masa kini.

programme.title: Beyond The Dream
programme.desc: Primary school teacher Lok is a recovering schizophrenic who falls in love with a young girl he first met. As he struggles to reveal his illness, Lok has a relapse and becomes delusional. Little does he know she is a mental health counsellor who has a hidden agenda. The pair develops a relationship that is beyond their wildest dreams.

programme.title: Infernal Affairs 2
programme.desc: In this prequel, the secrets of Infernal Affairs are revealed - the resentment between police superintendent Wong and crime boss Sam, as well as the beginning of the parallel fates of the two moles, Yan and Ming. The keys lie in the hands of Sam's wife, a ruthless kingpin and a righteous cop.

programme.title: Sex And The Beauties
programme.desc: It is said that Hong Kong is a sexy and sexual city where life is breathtakingly fast but glamorous. Fear of marriage, single & successful psychiatrist, Selina and other beauties seek for love and happy endings.

programme.title: Hell Hole
programme.desc: About three horror stories in different era: a pregnant woman haunted by a ghost, a boy commits suicide, and some company staff are haunted after they open a box of used clothes.

programme.title: Hell Hole
programme.desc: Berkisah tentang tiga cerita di era yang berbeda: seorang wanita hamil yang dihantui oleh arwah, seorang anak laki-laki yang bunuh diri, dan beberapa staf perusahaan yang dihantui setelah membuka sekotak pakaian bekas.

programme.title: 77 Heartwarmings
programme.desc: After breaking up with Adam, Eva focuses on her career but Adam still wants to make up and tries to move her 77 times. Things become more complicated when a Thai movie idol courts Eva. It is at this time that Evas mother becomes very ill, and she considers marriage in order to fulfil her mothers wish. Will Adam succeed in warming Evas heart?

programme.title: One Second
programme.desc: The film is set during the Cultural Revolution, where a common man escapes a labour camp to find a newsreel that captures his daughter for one second in a movie.

programme.title: One Second
programme.desc: Berlatar pada masa Revolusi Kebudayaan, film ini bercerita tentang seorang pria biasa yang melarikan diri dari kamp buruh untuk mencari sebuah tayangan berita yang merekam putrinya selama satu detik.

programme.title: CGTN Documentary
programme.desc: Launched on Jan. 1, 2011, CGTN Documentary is the only Chinese TV channel to broadcast documentaries in English 24/7. The channel broadcasts over 1,000 episodes of new programs each year, including top quality documentaries such as A Bite of China, Wild Wonders, and the 100-episode A History of China. CGTN Documentary is an ideal platform for people around the world to learn about China's past and present, and is dedicated to promoting the best of Chinese documentaries.
